      <title>中国考虑对普华永道因恒大审计工作开出创纪录罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/china-weighs-record-fine-for-pwc-over-evergrande-auditing-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国准备对普华永道处以创纪录的罚款，并暂停其部分本地业务，原因是普华永道涉嫌参与了中国最大的金融欺诈案之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/china-weighs-record-fine-for-pwc-over-evergrande-auditing-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 04:17:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约商品交易所空头挤压解除，铜价延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/aluminum-hits-two-year-high-as-china-capacity-limits-help-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着纽约期货市场历史性的空头逼空解除，铜价延续从纪录高位回落的势头。铝价从两年高位回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/aluminum-hits-two-year-high-as-china-capacity-limits-help-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 03:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
